Can Terraform Itself Ask for Approval?

No.

Terraform supports:

terraform plan
terraform apply
terraform destroy

It has no built-in manual approval mechanism.

Approval is handled by:

Azure DevOps
GitHub Actions
Jenkins
GitLab CI
Other CI/CD orchestration tools
